The Japanese Squiers made by Fender are the ones with the most excellent craftsmanship and are highly sought after for their rarity and high quality. They are made of heavy and high quality materials not the cheap ones like they do now. So get this truly incredible guitar for an absolute steal for a quick fix yourself or a short trip to the local guitar shop.
